net.objectzoo.events.impl

Interface Event0AsyncDelegate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Action0, Action0Async, Event0, Event0Delegate
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Event0AsyncAdapter

    public interface Event0AsyncDelegate
extends Action0Async, Event0Delegate
    An Event0AsyncDelegate implements Action0Async as well as Event0Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action0Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event0Delegate interface.
    Author:
    tilmann
